  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start your day with an excellent buffet breakfast - there's a range of hot and cold dishes on offer.</p>
<p>Complimentary cake and savoury snacks are served between 2-5pm each day (drinks not included).</p>
<p>The half board package also includes a delicious four-course meal - most will be served in the hotel's stylish <strong>Caesar Ritz</strong> restaurant. Here you'll be spoilt with the best regional and seasonal products, expertly cooked and served in a relaxed atmosphere. On the days when the Caesar Ritz restaurant is closed, your evening meal with be in the <strong>Del Ponte Pizzeria</strong>. Throughout the week, you can also opt to dine in one of the à la carte restaurants - you'll be credited CHF20 per person from the hotel bill.</p>
<p>After dinner, head to the hotel bar to enjoy an excellent selection of drinks (payable locally).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
