  <description><![CDATA[<p>If you're looking for the wow-factor, you're search ends here. Walliserhof Grand Hotel &amp; Spa combines luxury with homely charm. Arrive to a warm welcome, and enjoy exceptional service throughout your stay. Sustainability takes centre stage, and the hotel has earned a silver Ibex Fairstay certificate and a prestigious three-star Swisstainable certificate for its efforts.</p>
<h2>Delicious meals</h2>
<p>The food is exquisite, but the atmosphere is laid-back. The culinary highlight of your day will be the expertly prepared four-course evening meal, showcasing the finest seasonal and regional ingredients.</p>
<h2>Exceptional spa &amp; wellness facilities</h2>
<p>Unwind in the hotel's extensive spa, featuring a spacious indoor pool, Finnish and organic saunas, a steam room, and relaxation areas. Pamper yourself with a range of massage and beauty treatments (payable locally). There are even treatments specifically for kids, so everyone can enjoy a spot of indulgence.</p>]]></description>
